  <h1>Hosting Guide</h1>
  <p>The Global Day of Coderetreat has become a major worldwide software development event. As an organizer or facilitator of a coderetreat, you will help thousands of developers to improve their software development skills (which, in turn, will help to make the world a better place).
  <p>Below you will find important information about the Global Day of Coderetreat: everything you need in order to register, promote, and organize a great event. We regularly add new content so be sure to check back often!</p>
